---
import Button from "@/components/input/Button.astro";
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Contributing"
  description="参与 Fand Server 项目。"
  keywords={["fand", "minecraft", "contributing", "server"]}
  canonical="/contribute"
>
  <header class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 pt-32 pb-16 lg:pt-36">
    <div class="tech-label mb-4">CONTRIBUTING</div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-white md:text-6xl">参与 Fand Server</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
      目前最需要的是可复现的性能场景、原版语义回归用例、插件 API 反馈，以及对区块、实体、光照等热路径的实现审查。
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <Button variant="filled" href="https://github.com/MC20018/Fand" external>GitHub</Button>
      <Button variant="outlined" href="/software/fand">核心介绍</Button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-4 px-4 pb-20 md:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-white">性能样本</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-gray-400">矿车/TNT 堆叠、高速探索、红石机器、刷怪塔、区块加载尖峰。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-white">语义检查</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-gray-400">确认优化开启和关闭时，不出现隐藏玩法变化。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-white">API 反馈</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-gray-400">配置、日志、Tag、世界生成和插件生命周期接口。</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
